  USAGE: This template is used by the inventory generator to create
  a separate downloadable PDF in "Your Documents".

  DATA EXPECTED:
  - property_address: Full property address
  - landlord_name: Landlord/agent name
  - tenant_names: Array of tenant names or comma-separated string
  - tenancy_start_date: UK formatted date
  - inventory: { rooms: [...] } - wizard inventory data (optional)
  - meter_reading_gas, meter_reading_electric, meter_reading_water (optional)
  - current_date: For "generated on" timestamp
  - jurisdiction: england | wales | scotland | northern-ireland
  ============================================================================
--}}

